kuri
Homonym Number:
Word Class: noun
Sense Number:  1
Definition:[Ma.] 1. orig. dog brought by the Maori. 2. an early whaling ship-dog that bred onshore in the wild. 3. dog [often as goory.]


Origin: [none]
